c: 24
v: 58
t: "oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Lolani akapolo anu aamuna ndi aakazi ndi ana amene sanathe msinkhu kuti apemphe poyamba pa nthawi zitatu, musadapemphere pemphero la m’mawa kapena pamene mwavula zovala zanu masana chifukwa cha kutentha kapena mutatha kupemphera mapemphero a usiku. Izi ndi nthawi zitatu zokhala panokha. Palibe chifukwa kwa inu kapena kwa iwo kuchezerana, wina ndi mnzake mu nthawi zina kupatula nthawi zimene zatchulidwazi. Kotero Mulungu amaulula poyera chivumbulutso chake kwa inu. Ndipo Mulungu ndi Wodziwa ndi Waluntha"